{"lemma":"خُدْعَةٌ","slug":"خُدْعَةٌ","root":"خ.د.ع","root_slug":"خ-د-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-د-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10128"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trick, deception","examples":[{"text":"هُوَ مُتَوَتِّرٌ وَلٰكِنَّهُ مُتَحَمِّسٌ لِتَقْدِيمِ خُدَعِهِ السِّحْرِيَّةِ فِي حَفْلَةِ عِيدِ الْمِيلَادِ.","english":"He's nervous but eager to debut his magic tricks at the birthday party."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xud.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10128","headword_ar":"خُدْعَةٌ","root":"xdE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing by which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which, one deceives, deludes, beguiles, circumvents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outwits;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb;) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEobapN","text_ar":"لُعْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies “ a thing with which one plays. ” (Msb.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadoEapN","text_ar":"خَدْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whom people deceive, delude, beguile, circumvent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outwit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEonapN","text_ar":"لُعْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies one “ who is much cursed. ” (TA.) [See, again,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadoEapN","text_ar":"خَدْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". The comparison of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xudoEapN","text_ar":"خُدْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in one sense with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEobapN","text_ar":"لُعْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in another sense with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luEonapN","text_ar":"لُعْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", suggests that one of the explanations above may perhaps be founded upon a mistranscription. On"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEolapN","text_ar":"فُعْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the measure of a word having the sense of a pass. part. n., see a remark of IB voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqaTN","text_ar":"لَقَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xadiyEapN","text_ar":"خَدِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}